reviewText: What an incredible movie. Thank you.
Real food for thought!  Well done!

In spite of leaning somewhat towards LDS beliefs, this is a very well presented documentary on near death experiences/phenomenon. The people who were interviewed told compelling stories regarding their NDE and were interesting to hear. While they incorperated some religion into the documentary they also presented the scientific views/opinions as well. Very well done overall, and I highly recommend this DVD to anyone interested in NDE studies.
Clear, concise, thorough study of the subject.  Very interesting and offering great peace.
Very interesting.  The personal stories are good.
